text: Hey Ryan! Sorry about the radio silence on my end so far this year. Finally coming up for air after delivering a few big jobs! How's the term been for you so far? Any work you can share with me? I'd love to see how you're getting on and what sort of skill level you're at so I can come up with a suitable mentorship plan moving forward!
(And by work I don't mean like shiny finished products, necessarily! Work that shows progress is perfect at this point- wireframe models, doodles, anything really :slightly_smiling_face:)
